yTime":"2019-06-25T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"緊係抵讚喇，真心相信嘅怕做，辛苦各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942fb2d3a52a1336bf62c4a42227ae6ac82ecfdb","tid":1256800,"uid":113155,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"香港仔傳單奇遇記<br />\n講左賤廢佬先 聲大夾惡<br />\n 有個又肥又廢嘅廢佬睇完之後鬧我 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擾民啊你哋成班 系度搞事<br />\n我一開始好好脾氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />指住傳單 所以對唔住啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗對唔住 你地擾民啊 做咩帶口罩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 病左啊 唔好意思<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班搞亂檔  慳啲啦（手指指）落雨啦 返屋企啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係啊 落雨啦 你都早啲返屋企<br />\n<br />\n仲有個老人家扯住我傾左半個鐘 聽左好耐我先知佢立場係踩政府 但同送中係off topic<br />\n<br />\n仲有小量廢佬企系度睇完 隊返備我唔要啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />備返你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然仲有支持我哋嘅人啦<br />\n我哋2人系樹底草叢附近派 好多蚊咬 有個姐姐見到 特登去買左支蚊怕水備我哋（應該特登去買 新包裝黎）好感動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有巿民睇完備返 以為佢又想屌7我啦 點知佢話 <br />\n你冇對唔住我 備返你備有需要嘅人啦 加油！<br />\n<br />\n仲有巿民會同我地講加油 我備廢佬diu7果陣 有巿 民大聲支援 廢佬先走左"},{"pid":"1a7dbac6125d4da7006caf49dce164195a05037b","tid":1256800,"uid":259121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb3544b2f16369a9764893b9676e8858d7956c","tid":1256800,"uid":170121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2895370