>\n<br />\n仲有個老人家扯住我傾左半個鐘 聽左好耐我先知佢立場係踩政府 但同送中係off topic<br />\n<br />\n仲有小量廢佬企系度睇完 隊返備我唔要啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />備返你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然仲有支持我哋嘅人啦<br />\n我哋2人系樹底草叢附近派 好多蚊咬 有個姐姐見到 特登去買左支蚊怕水備我哋（應該特登去買 新包裝黎）好感動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有巿民睇完備返 以為佢又想屌7我啦 點知佢話 <br />\n你冇對唔住我 備返你備有需要嘅人啦 加油！<br />\n<br />\n仲有巿民會同我地講加油 我備廢佬diu7果陣 有巿 民大聲支援 廢佬先走左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d116ed8f535c52a36c7120219fb906d4a90af92","tid":1256800,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13db7915826fc95bcf1bf3dd341d5c398e1ca089","tid":1256800,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"乜撚野垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2dcf9ba6064dd7825db851afb657ba60e491fd9","tid":1256800,"uid":185925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e2123cfb5b6fd5f53e11170062807557ddc95e","tid":1256800,"uid":122185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"圍稅局失敗，相信當日企出來義士們一定會好灰心。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">正所謂綠帽唔怕戴，最緊要除得快！</span><br />\n今日的道歉運動正正反映香港人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">能夠從錯誤中學習，不斷變通</span></span>。<br />\n好快又可以捲土重來！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79ad59de741221619f7bfc37b5557ec611235e7","tid":1256800,"uid":40606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:00:53.000Z",